{"tid":2460483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"復必泰疫苗｜科興如常接種　有市民稱無影響信心","createTime":"2021-03-25T01:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T09:21:33.000Z","uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6f5ab88c0d5b92e7e36f220039188d5b0640ce","tid":2460483,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"政府昨日起，暫停接種BioNTech復必泰新冠疫苗，科興疫苗則如常接種。在接種科興疫苗的佐敦官涌體育館疫苗接種中心，有長者指因為較相信國家，一早已選擇接種科興，到現在才有時間接種，昨日的事件無影響整體對疫苗信心，亦有市民指，出現問題的只是復必泰疫苗，對科興仍有信心。 亦有從事飲食業的外籍人士指，原本預約下星期一接種第一劑復必泰疫苗，現時感到困惑和失望，因原本希望接種疫苗後，可減少檢測次數，但仍未決定會否改為接種科興。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2384464&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=f7739a50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384464</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaftyB1KPVyUWL4Ya7tKD87hWSAYYetmFBqhfLXZ3QbEC?filename=RRGk7Za.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRRGk7Za.jpg&h=bc11845d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbe8248326a5736596f979bc2e8dfa8e81a047f5","tid":2460483,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:09:52.000Z","msg":"無信心何來影響"},{"pid":"75b4dff151d883c97cd4715515f1a4df86233417","tid":2460483,"uid":8647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:20:49.000Z","msg":"平時話自己中立果啲9成係呢啲藍屍，今朝聽個contractar car 司機話之後會打four 興<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問佢科興有咩好，點解打科興又答唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07246658fadd10d9d3da533c931cb37fddb42482","tid":2460483,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"打完幾時可以除罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d5356b2e551d9d09fb1648a9c86827a2a7034d","tid":2460483,"uid":110832,"like":0,"d